{"tid":317134,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONE PIECE/海賊王 872 漫畫情報","createTime":"2017-07-11T08:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T02:06:05.000Z","uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8907047d20f9c647f59d82ec09f00bc7f167a8c4","tid":317134,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://imgur.com/a/bLY2R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FbLY2R&d=lov1Do8XFtxWa9%2BicBDhuNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=537b01d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/bLY2R</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://onepiece-naruto.com/onepiece/post-7417/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonepiece-naruto.com%2Fonepiece%2Fpost-7417%2F&d=lov1Do8XFtxWa9%2BicBDhuNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5f5bf1bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://onepiece-naruto.com/onepiece/post-7417/</a><br />\n第872話　とろふわ<br />\n<br />\n倒壊する城<br />\n混乱する一同だがこのドサクサに紛れベッジらは脱出に成功する<br />\nベッジは暗殺するまでもない。やつらは全員城の倒壊に巻き込まれ死ぬだろうと高を括る<br />\nだがシュトロイゼンの能力で城は本物のホールケーキになりマム達は瓦礫に押しつぶされることなく全員生還<br />\n<br />\nルフィとベッジは互いの武運を祈りつつそれぞれの船へ<br />\nそのころマムに異変<br />\nウェディングケーキを食べ損ねたマムは食いわずらいの症状を発症する<br />\n<br />\n次週へ"},{"pid":"2c342bfc3f886fdee38e2ee42d86d0015c1286bb","tid":317134,"uid":51652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"又休刊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5ab6c9b43df3c46c82bf0fc14261fb6bdb2a02","tid":317134,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"872話 軟綿綿<br />\n倒塌的城堡<br />\n雖然大家都陷入了混亂，但貝基他們也趁著混亂的時候逃了出來<br />\n貝基輕視的說這根本沒有暗殺的必要，他們全員都會被捲入城堡的倒塌中然後直接死掉<br />\n但是修特羅伊森用能力把城堡變成了真正的whole cake，big mom他們並沒有被瓦礫壓住，全員生還<br />\n路飛和貝基互相祝福對方的武運然後各自回到了船上<br />\n就在這時候big mom產生了異變<br />\n因為婚禮蛋糕沒吃到就給毀了，big mom的暴食症發作<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9b0dcc80401ea56738b938555ff8552a677bfe99","tid":317134,"uid":101309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"唔通之後食撚曬啲仔女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df95970e659c98fd029e41466001ec0820ff41a","tid":317134,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}